name: Sean Has To Go
description:
✦--------------------------------------------------------------------------✦
Download .exe or run in full-screen for best experience!
✦--------------------------------------------------------------------------✦

✦------- How to play! -------✦

- Arrow Keys to move

- Z key to jump

- Up arrow to climb ladders & ropes

- Down arrow to crouch

✦--------------------------------------------------------------------------✦

This game is a submission for Beginners Circle Jam 3.

Created by:

Hendrick White 'Blackisshh' - itch, twitter

Adam Molina 'Aisem' - itch, twitter, facebook

Miguel Velez 'Vezdoor' - itch, youtube
